.08-1.62 0-5 0-5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-0\"><h4 class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white leading-tight\">서비스 완성</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-tight\">완성도 높은 실제 프로덕트 구축</p></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-3 mt-1 border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between bg-emerald-600/5 dark:bg-emerald-500/10 rounded-xl px-3 py-2 border border-emerald-500/10\"><span class=\"text-[12px] font-bold text-emerald-600/70 dark:text-emerald-400/70 uppercase\">Goal</span><span class=\"text-[12px] font-black text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200\">실제 서비스 배포</span></div></div></div></div></div></header><main class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full px-6 py-10 space-y-8\"><div class=\"bg-card rounded-xl border border-border p-2 flex items-center gap-2 overflow-x-auto shadow-sm no-scrollbar transition-colors relative z-20\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 px-4 whitespace-nowrap group cursor-pointer\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layout-grid w-4 h-4 text-slate-400\"><rect width=\"7\" height=\"7\" x=\"3\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"7\" x=\"14\" y=\"3\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"7\" x=\"14\" y=\"14\" rx=\"1\"></rect><rect width=\"7\" height=\"7\" x=\"3\" y=\"14\" rx=\"1\"></rect></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">커리큘럼 로드맵</span></div><div class=\"h-6 w-[1px] bg-slate-100 dark:bg-white/10 mx-2\"></div><a class=\"block shrink-0\" href=\"/curriculum\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 px-6 py-2 rounded-xl transition-all cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 text-slate-400\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">1. 입문</span><span class=\"text-[12px] whitespace-nowrap text-slate-400\">Mindset &amp; Comm.</span></div></a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 text-slate-200 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"block shrink-0\" href=\"/curriculum/basic\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 px-6 py-2 rounded-xl transition-all cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 text-slate-400\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">2. 기초</span><span class=\"text-[12px] whitespace-nowrap text-slate-400\">System &amp; Structure</span></div></a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 text-slate-200 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"block shrink-0\" href=\"/curriculum/practice\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 px-6 py-2 rounded-xl transition-all cursor-pointer bg-emerald-600 text-white shadow-lg shadow-emerald-600/20 scale-105\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-white\">3. 실전</span><span class=\"text-[12px] whitespace-nowrap text-emerald-200\">Execution &amp; Build</span></div></a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 text-slate-200 shrink-0\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"block shrink-0\" href=\"/curriculum/advanced\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-0.5 px-6 py-2 rounded-xl transition-all cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 text-slate-400\"><span class=\"text-xs font-black text-slate-400\">4. 심화</span><span class=\"text-[12px] whitespace-nowrap text-slate-400\">Scale &amp; Real World</span></div></a></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start\"><aside class=\"lg:col-span-3 space-y-6 sticky top-24\"><div class=\"bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden shadow-sm transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"p-5 border-b border-border bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-slate-800/50 flex flex-col gap-1 transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-emerald-600 text-white w-5 h-5 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-[12px]\">3</span>실전 단계</h3><p class=\"text-[12px] text-emerald-500 font-bold\">&quot;실제로 결과물을 만드는 단계&quot;</p></div><div class=\"divide-y divide-border\"><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all bg-emerald-600/10 border-r-4 border-emerald-600 \"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-xs text-emerald-600\">핵심 주제 (Core)</span><div class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-600\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 \"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">선택형 프로젝트 트랙</span></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-white/5 py-1\"><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 A: 웹 서비스</span></div><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 B: 자동화 툴</span></div><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 C: 크롬 확장</span></div><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 D: AI 서비스</span></div><div class=\"p-4 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer transition-all hover:bg-slate-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 pl-9 py-2.5\"><span class=\"font-bold transition-colors text-[12px] text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\">트랙 E: 콘텐츠 플랫폼</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 space-y-6 shadow-sm transition-colors text-left\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><h3 class=\"font-bold text-sm text-slate-800 dark:text-white flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-lg\">🎁</span> 실전 프로젝트 가이드</h3></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">본인의 관심 분야나 비즈니스 목표에 맞는 트랙을 선택하세요. 1개 이상의 프로젝트 완성을 권장합니다.</p><div class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">실질적인 포트폴리오 확보</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">상용화 가능한 수준의 개발</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 group cursor-default\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-3 h-3 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0 transition-transform group-hover:scale-125\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 group-hover:text-slate-800 dark:group-hover:text-slate-200 transition-colors leading-tight\">보안 및 운영 기초 습득</span></li></div></div></div></aside><div class=\"lg:col-span-9 space-y-16\"><div class=\"bg-card rounded-2xl border border-border p-8 shadow-sm space-y-12 transition-colors\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-4 pb-8 border-b border-border text-left\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-600 text-[12px] font-black px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Execution &amp; Build</span></div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white tracking-tight\">3. 실전: 프로덕트 빌딩</h2><p class=\"text-emerald-600 font-bold text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">&quot;실제로 결과물을 만드는 단계&quot;</p><p class=\"text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm\">설계를 넘어 실제 사용자가 사용할 수 있는 어플리케이션을 구축합니다.<br/>보안, 일관성, 확장성을 고려한 프로급 개발 프로세스를 경험하세요.</p></div></div><div id=\"core\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 space-y-6 text-left\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-layers\"><path d=\"M12.83 2.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 6.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.83l8.58 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0l8.58-3.9a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.83z\"></path><path d=\"M2 12a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 12\"></path><path d=\"M2 17a1 1 0 0 0 .58.91l8.6 3.91a2 2 0 0 0 1.65 0l8.58-3.9A1 1 0 0 0 22 17\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">핵심 주제 (Common Core)</h3></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors\">프로젝트 구조 설계</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">유지보수가 쉬운 파일 구조와 컴포넌트 분리 전략</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors\">코드 일관성 유지 전략</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">린트 설정 및 팀 협업을 위한 코드 컨벤션 수립</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors\">서브도메인 &amp; 이메일 관리</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">서브도메인 할당 원리 및 브랜드 이메일 계정 생성/관리</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors\">디자인 명시도 개선</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">UI 가독성과 사용성을 높이는 디테일한 CSS/UX 튜닝</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors\">API 활용 및 에러 처리</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">외부 서비스 연동 시 발생할 수 있는 예외 상황 대응</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all flex items-start gap-4 group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500 mt-0.5 shrink-0\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-1 group-hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors\">보안 기초 (.env, 인증)</h4><p class=\"text-[12px] text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">API 키 관리 및 사용자 인증(Auth) 시스템의 기본 보안</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-4 border-t border-border text-left\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-6\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-teal-50 dark:bg-teal-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-box\"><path d=\"M21 8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16Z\"></path><path d=\"m3.3 7 8.7 5 8.7-5\"></path><path d=\"M12 22V12\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white\">선택형 프로젝트 트랙 (Optional Projects)</h3></div><div class=\"space-y-12\"><div id=\"track-a\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-emerald-100 dark:border-emerald-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-emerald-500 transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-emerald-50 dark:bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track A</div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-monitor w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500\"><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"3\" rx=\"2\"></rect><line x1=\"8\" x2=\"16\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"21\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"17\" y2=\"21\"></line></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">웹 서비스 트랙</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">수익화가 가능한 SaaS 형태의 웹 어플리케이션을 구축합니다.</p></div><ul class=\"space-y-3 pt-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> 로그인 및 회원가입 연동</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 text-emerald-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> 사용자 데이터 영구 저장 및 관리</li></ul><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-emerald-600 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-emerald-500 transition-all\">웹 프로젝트 시작</button></div><div id=\"track-b\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-blue-100 dark:border-blue-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track B</div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-code w-5 h-5 text-blue-500\"><polyline points=\"16 18 22 12 16 6\"></polyline><polyline points=\"8 6 2 12 8 18\"></polyline></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">자동화 툴 트랙</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">일상의 불편함을 해결하는 맞춤형 업무 자동화 프로그램을 제작합니다.</p></div><ul class=\"space-y-3 pt-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 text-blue-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> 웹 크롤링 및 데이터 전처리</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 text-blue-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> 주기적 태스크 실행 및 리포트 발송</li></ul><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-blue-600 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-blue-500 transition-all\">자동화 툴 시작</button></div><div id=\"track-c\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-purple-100 dark:border-purple-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-purple-500 transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-purple-50 dark:bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track C</div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-5 h-5 text-purple-500\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">크롬 확장 프로그램</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">브라우저 기능을 확장하여 생산성을 높이는 익스텐션을 개발합니다.</p></div><ul class=\"space-y-3 pt-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 text-purple-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> 브라우저 탭 및 DOM 조작 기초</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 text-purple-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> 확장 프로그램 전용 UI 및 백그라운드 스크립트</li></ul><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-purple-600 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-purple-500 transition-all\">확장 프로그램 시작</button></div><div id=\"track-d\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-orange-100 dark:border-orange-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-orange-500 transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-orange-50 dark:bg-orange-500/10 text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track D</div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-bot w-5 h-5 text-orange-500\"><path d=\"M12 8V4H8\"></path><rect width=\"16\" height=\"12\" x=\"4\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M2 14h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 14h2\"></path><path d=\"M15 13v2\"></path><path d=\"M9 13v2\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-slate-800 dark:text-white mb-2\">AI 서비스 트랙</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed\">최신 AI API를 연동하여 지능형 챗봇이나 생성 서비스를 구축합니다.</p></div><ul class=\"space-y-3 pt-2\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 text-orange-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> 스트리밍 응답 처리 및 대화 이력 관리</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 text-orange-500\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg> 지능형 에이전트 서비스 기획 및 연동</li></ul><button class=\"w-full py-4 bg-orange-600 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-orange-500 transition-all\">AI 서비스 시작</button></div><div id=\"track-e\" class=\"scroll-mt-32 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-3xl border-2 border-indigo-100 dark:border-indigo-500/20 p-8 space-y-6 hover:border-indigo-500 transition-all group shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex bg-indigo-50 dark:bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400 text-[12px] font-black px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-widest\">Track E</div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-newspaper w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500\"><path d=\"M4 22h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 1-2 2Zm0 0a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-9c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h2\"></path><path d=\"M18 14h-8\"></path><path d=\"M15 18h-5\"></path><path d=\"M10 6h8v4h-8V6Z\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 cla